{"about_the_game":"The foreman has had enough. He\u2019s taken a lot of crap from<br>the boss over at Mega Dump Corp. Now it is your turn<br>to turn a ruined outfit into a thriving business and <br>restore the health of the planet! As you grow your operation bigger,<br>you will take on challenges on other planets. Beware though,<br>a dark secret lurks on the planet\u2019s surface.  <br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268360/extras/thegame3.png?t=1625085788\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268360/extras/ezgif.com-video-to-gif.gif?t=1625085788\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268360/extras/EA-banner.png?t=1625085788\" /><br><br>Trashed is a garbage management action adventure.<br><br>You can build structures for waste management from a <br>3rd person (Top Down) perspective and then protect them with various<br>weapons that you can find or buy on the planet.<br><br>Use vehicles to traverse the surface of each planet faster, or to<br>help you push trash into incinerators or recyclers. <br><br>Take care of the planet, and you will see it return to its original glory.<br>Follow an interesting storyline that evolves as take on new missions<br>and contracts.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268360/extras/features.png?t=1625085788\" /><br><br>Unique Waste Management system<br>Planet Terraforming<br>Day/Night System<br>Top Down/3rd person Combat/Action<br>3 different planets to explore<br>Special weapons and upgrades for each planet<br>Strategy based building<br>Lots of exploring, unique items to find<br>Various vehicles to use and operate","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1268360?t=1625085788","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.ste